00:01:07,020 --> 00:01:09,110
[Dawn is Breaking]

2
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:11,760
[Adapted from Fanqie Novel
After the Obsessed State Preceptor's Takeover]

3
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:16,410
[Episode 30]
[White Hair]

4
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,720
This is indeed Red Spiderwort.

5
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,200
Li Chi's countless calculations

6
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:23,960
failed to account

7
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:25,040
for this small sachet.

8
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,880
It's barely enough
to make the antidote.

9
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:32,760
What should we do?

10
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,200
Jiang Yan's poison has flared up.

11
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:40,960
What's happening?

12
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,440
Yin.

13
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,320
Master, have you lost your mind?

14
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,480
We only have one antidote
made from Red Spiderwort.

15
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:56,560
Are you...

16
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,440
Save Jiang Yan.

17
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:02,920
No way.

18
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,680
This won't work.

19
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,280
We can't sacrifice you

20
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,040
to save the child.

21
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:07,720
There must be another way.

22
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:11,360
Jiang Yan's poisoning isn't as serious.

23
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,840
This antidote could be split
into two doses.

24
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,640
No.

25
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:18,840
The ingredients in the formula
are very strong.

26
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,360
Without Red Spiderwort as a catalyst,

27
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:23,280
it becomes a fatal poison.

28
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:26,720
The amount of Red Spiderwort
can only save one person.

29
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,280
Tinghan,

30
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:34,920
you don't think I'm acting
out of kindness to save him, do you?

31
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,280
I'm saving myself.

32
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:43,840
Yin.

33
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:48,560
Tinghan,

34
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:51,080
fulfill his wish.

35
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,120
Yin.

36
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:54,720
He only wants to pass on
a new life to Jiang Yan.

37
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:58,280
This was his unfulfilled wish
from years ago.

38
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,400
Yin,

39
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,920
I want to go home.

40
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,160
Alright,

41
00:03:20,210 --> 00:03:22,400
♪The wind under the eaves♪

42
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,280
we'll go home.

43
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,510
♪Gently taps on the wooden door♪

44
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:28,600
Let's go.

45
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:32,420
♪The night is at its peak♪

46
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,530
♪A thunderclap rolls♪

47
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,460
♪Stirring up old dreams again♪

48
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:43,960
♪Thoughts linger
on the warmth of the past♪

49
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:47,390
♪The sincerity of the past♪

50
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:50,740
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

51
00:03:51,010 --> 00:03:54,010
♪But soon they cool♪

52
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:58,250
♪I watch as you pass by♪

53
00:03:58,270 --> 00:04:01,360
♪Not daring to ask♪

54
00:04:01,890 --> 00:04:05,180
♪Like the moon, waxing and waning♪

55
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:08,250
♪How could it ask more?♪

56
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:13,440
♪You and I are like a small boat
on the river♪

57
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:18,450
♪Rising and falling with the waves♪

58
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:36,700
♪Speaking of love and hate♪

59
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:39,530
♪How can I distinguish them?♪

60
00:04:41,430 --> 00:04:43,820
♪Longing for fate, praying sincerely♪

61
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:47,170
♪Yet the world does not acknowledge it♪

62
00:04:48,230 --> 00:04:50,590
♪The night grows deep♪

63
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,830
♪Old dreams are stirred again♪

64
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:58,040
♪Yet the previous ones
are still within them♪

65
00:04:58,230 --> 00:05:01,300
♪Why do they remain silent?♪

66
00:05:01,620 --> 00:05:04,720
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

67
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:08,130
♪But soon they cool♪

68
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:12,310
♪I look, adding a few more strokes
to the word "love"♪

69
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:15,450
♪A new year's ring♪

70
00:05:15,770 --> 00:05:19,080
♪The cicada's cry is close,
autumn leaves are near♪

71
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:22,250
♪Yet it's hard to recognize each other♪

72
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:27,460
♪I sigh, why are you and I♪

73
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:32,570
♪Rising and falling,
drifting in this way?♪

74
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:07,720
Is it beautiful?

75
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,040
Yes.

76
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:13,560
You're very graceful

77
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,840
and the sword moves like a dragon.

78
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:19,560
I meant

79
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,960
if the flower is beautiful.

80
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,520
Yes.

81
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,000
You can't see, can you?

82
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,720
The poison has already entered his body.

83
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:36,000
It starts with the hair and eyes,

84
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:40,640
then moves to the ears,
nose and internal organs,

85
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,200
and finally the limbs and bones

86
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,560
until death.

87
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,640
I'll check the medical texts again

88
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,280
to see if there are other remedies.

89
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,200
You know what?

90
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,960
Outside of Zhangzhou,

91
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,640
when I woke up,

92
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,960
I recognized you instantly.

93
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:34,240
♪The wind blows cool in autumn again♪

94
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:40,200
If I had quietly approached you,

95
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,440
would you've recognized me?

96
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,880
You hated me then.

97
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:49,840
Since you recognized me,

98
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:52,200
why didn't you drive me away immediately

99
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:55,370
♪Believing a heartfelt connection
would last♪

100
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,520
or kill me?

101
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:00,400
I...

102
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,760
I didn't dare to admit it.

103
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,720
I despised myself

104
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,520
while unwilling to expose you.

105
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,280
Na Jinci,

106
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,720
even when I'm watching you,

107
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,760
I still miss you.

108
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:25,000
♪Love, hate, joy, sorrow,
he dares not taste again♪

109
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,880
Since we parted,

110
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:30,400
I hadn't stopped thinking
about you for a moment.

111
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:33,400
♪Witnessing the fleeting affairs
of the world♪

112
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,760
Yin,

113
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,400
this life

114
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,200
is too short.

115
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,680
From now on, we won't be separated.

116
00:09:58,150 --> 00:10:01,130
♪In old age, we speak of fervent love♪

117
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:05,250
♪The years and seasons have burned us♪

118
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:07,070
♪What I fear most
is rain falling into my eyes♪

119
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:10,200
♪Too many things are hard to conceal♪

120
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:13,460
♪Brewed into tears♪

121
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:15,510
♪He, with no time to spare, should be♪

122
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,770
♪Grass and trees, untouched by harm♪

123
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:21,890
♪Yet he ventured into the tumult
of the world, taking a journey♪

124
00:10:22,210 --> 00:10:25,770
♪He's like the moon falling
into the dust, full of desolation♪

125
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:26,800
Miss.

126
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:31,200
Pei Che.

127
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,480
You're still alive?

128
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:33,800
What are you doing here?

129
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:37,600
How come you're so petty?

130
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:38,960
What am I doing here?

131
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:40,680
To deliver medicine.

132
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:41,600
I brought you medicine.

133
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,000
This is...

134
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,600
It's called Winter Glory Flower.

135
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,360
I heard he's dying,

136
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,920
so I specially had someone find it.

137
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,920
Although it's highly toxic,

138
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,840
compared to Red Spiderwort,

139
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,800
it can provide
about ten to twelve percent

140
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,080
of the effect as a catalyst.

141
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:58,600
Really?

142
00:10:59,240 --> 00:10:59,800
Thank you, Pei Che.

143
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,360
Don't thank me yet, miss.

144
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,720
Death is still inevitable.

145
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,720
Although Winter Glory Flower is useful,

146
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:10,000
it's also highly toxic.

147
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:13,160
Once ingested,

148
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:15,320
it restores sight instantly

149
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,960
but will make one
lose all martial skills

150
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,200
and become a cripple.

151
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,800
Moreover, it only prolongs life
for six months.

152
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:25,600
If you can't find Red Spiderwort
within six months,

153
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:27,080
even the gods can't save him.

154
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,320
And miss,

155
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,440
you might not know,

156
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,040
but Red Spiderwort

157
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,960
takes ten years to grow a single plant.

158
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,240
Finding one

159
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:36,960
would be a miracle.

160
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:40,920
We'll only have six months.

161
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,680
That's enough.

162
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,320
Even if we can't find Red Spiderwort,

163
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,920
didn't we agree?

164
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,200
Being together for a day

165
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,720
brings happiness for a day.

166
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,680
Alright,

167
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,320
once you're better,

168
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,960
we'll immediately set out
to find Red Spiderwort.

169
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,080
Coincidentally,

170
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,200
Red Spiderwort grows in the desert.

171
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:06,080
I'm familiar with the terrain

172
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,720
and have manpower.

173
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:09,040
There's no need for him.

174
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,840
It's inconvenient for him
to move around.

175
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:11,720
Miss, I'll go with you...

176
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,440
Xiao Zhi,

177
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,920
see off the guest.

178
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:25,200
The journey will be long and arduous

179
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:27,040
and the desert is extremely dangerous.

180
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,200
With your current condition,

181
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,480
I can only be rest assured

182
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,480
if you bring more people.

183
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,360
Now that the enemies
have been eliminated,

184
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:38,040
we'll travel light

185
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,320
and comfortably.

186
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:43,080
Moreover, my time is limited.

187
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,320
This journey,

188
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,120
I want to go with her

189
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,800
and let her live the life
she's always wanted.

190
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,200
Regardless of the outcome,

191
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:54,840
I have no regrets.

192
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:58,360
We'll travel together

193
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:01,240
like an ordinary couple in Yu.

194
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:02,800
From now on,

195
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:03,840
the road ahead will be smooth.

196
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,840
Master,

197
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:09,960
at least let me see you off
one last time.

198
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:15,600
The Emperor won't last three months.

199
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:17,840
If he passes away,

200
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:19,600
the court will be in turmoil.

201
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,680
Andu will be the most dangerous place.

202
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:23,920
Xiao Zhi,

203
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:25,920
from today on,

204
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:28,440
you're the head of the Jade Pavilion.

205
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,440
You must fully assist Tinghan

206
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,440
and help Jiang Yan ascend the throne.

207
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:37,640
Master,

208
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,240
I...

209
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,440
Jade Pavilion is my lifelong work.

210
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:44,480
Entrusting it to you gives me
peace of mind.

211
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:47,840
Yes.

212
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,560
After today,

213
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,200
we should all take care of ourselves.

214
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,200
Whether I die or not,

215
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:01,600
we won't return.

216
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,200
Everything will be better.

217
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:10,440
There's a vast world
beyond the Great Wall.

218
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:13,440
We'll meet again.

219
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,160
Tinghan,

220
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:20,720
take care.

221
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:22,920
Take care.

222
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:41,440
[Six Months Later]

223
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:51,640
I hold a high position

224
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:53,280
but have acted recklessly,

225
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:55,280
causing loyal officials to be wronged

226
00:14:55,280 --> 00:14:57,240
and corrupt officials to rise.

227
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:59,720
The sins are mine alone to bear

228
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:01,720
and I dare not pardon myself.

229
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:04,120
Today, I express deep remorse
for the past

230
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:06,720
and will abdicate
and retreat to a separate palace,

231
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:09,000
passing the throne to another.

232
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,920
Inspector Governor Na Cheng'an,

233
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,280
known for his integrity,

234
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:14,640
was slandered by malicious rumors.

235
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:16,760
Today, he's reinstated

236
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,480
and posthumously honored as Wenzhen.

237
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:23,000
General Xie Tinghan is promoted
to Duke of the State

238
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:25,800
and will assist the new Emperor
in governing the state.

239
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:32,590
[By Imperial Decree]

240
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:48,200
Long live the Emperor!

241
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,200
The moon beyond the Great Wall
is so beautiful.

242
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:22,600
Unfortunately, Yue can't see it
with her own eyes.

243
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:26,200
In the realm of the underworld,

244
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,720
we'll always meet again.

245
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:30,800
When that time comes,

246
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:36,200
I'll admire all the scenery

247
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,080
and travel the world with you.

248
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:46,440
Will you always be with me?

249
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:51,680
I'm a demon risen from hell.

250
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,480
Once you're entangled with me,

251
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,600
you'll never be able to shake me off

252
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,480
in all your lifetimes.

253
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:23,720
Na Jinci,

254
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:31,920
from today on,

255
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,680
I'll be your wife.

256
00:17:37,280 --> 00:17:38,800
Now that we're married,

257
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:42,280
you don't need to wander anymore.

258
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:49,600
I'll be with you

259
00:17:50,320 --> 00:17:51,520
through the seasons.

260
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:58,240
Yin,

261
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:03,200
I want

262
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,240
to be with you always.

263
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,160
Always with you.

264
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:17,820
[Na Family Ancestral Hall]
[Honor ancestors, respect the elders]

