♪The night is at its peak♪

269
00:18:59,350 --> 00:19:01,600
♪A thunderclap rolls♪

270
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:04,530
♪Stirring up old dreams again♪

271
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:07,200
It's so big and round.

272
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:11,320
Look at the stars next to it.

273
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:14,480
It's not as big as that one.

274
00:19:14,800 --> 00:19:15,560
Look.

275
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:19,080
♪But soon they cool♪

276
00:19:19,630 --> 00:19:23,320
♪I watch as you pass by♪

277
00:19:23,340 --> 00:19:26,430
♪Not daring to ask♪

278
00:19:29,360 --> 00:19:31,160
Look at that one.

279
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:33,160
That one?

280
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,520
